org.bamja.core.annotations
Annotation Type NoneComponent

public @interface NoneComponent

This annotation says to the bamja core that no components are to be manage. If a component defined parallel, then bamja ignored this annotation. Attention: If this annotation is present, a xml file is ignored too.

Since:
Version: 0.1.0 (20.02.2006)
